title: List of tallest structures in Turkmenistan
text:
This is a list of the tallest structures in <a href="Turkmenistan">Turkmenistan</a>. This list contains all tower, buildings and other structures in Turkmenistan based on standard height.
Tallest structures.
This list ranks the structures in <a href="Turkmenistan">Turkmenistan</a> that stand at least 90 m (295 ft). Only completed buildings and structured are included.
